# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# RHOBEAR Designs — Cloud (Free + Pro) build-time env.
#
# These are BUILD-TIME constants (Vite inlines import.meta.env.VITE_* into the
# static dist). They are NOT secrets — the bundle is public. Every value has a
# safe default so the editor builds with `npm run build` even when none are set.
#
# Live secrets (Stripe secret key, provider API keys, DB url, session secret)
# live on the FAMILY backend (rhobear-plans board-render) as server env — the
# owner inserts them there. Designs itself ships ZERO secrets. See DEPLOY.md.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# The RHOBEAR house LLM gateway (OpenAI-compatible). Default '' = same-origin
# /v1 (Caddy reverse-proxies it in prod; Vite proxies it in dev). Set this only
# for a split-origin deploy where the gateway lives at its own host.
# Example: VITE_MANAGED_BASE=https://gw.rhobear.ai
VITE_MANAGED_BASE=

# The family backend API root (auth + gate + billing). Default '' = same-origin
# /cloud/* (Caddy reverse-proxies it). Set for a split-origin deploy.
# Example: VITE_CLOUD_API_BASE=https://api.rhobear.ai
VITE_CLOUD_API_BASE=
